reviewText: Haven't seen this in ages it's a shame that it never made it to DVD let alone more episodes of it

Thanks so much for having a copy of Mad Scientist!!!! This was the best thing that I have been able to find!!!! This silly silly tape was a favorite for my sibling and she liked it so much that the tape eventually stopped working!!! I gave this tape to her as a gift and she was sooo happy!!! Shed loved it so much!!! Thank you for having it!!!
